title: Grid of circles with 50m radius for St. Georg (n=570)
name: Grid of circles with 50m radius for St. Georg (n=570)
description:
Dataset created by adding a buffer of 50m around the features in 'Grid for St. Georg (n=570)'

This dataset forms a grid of circles (due to distortion from map proyection they look like ellipses) laid out over St. Georg (Hamburg, Germany) from

latitude 53.549 to 53.566 North and
longitude 9.998 to 10.027 East.

Intersections are named A1 to S30 with a total n of 570 (=19*30)

Sources: 
Dataset: Grid for St. Georg (n=570)
geocommons.com/overlays/205304
